{"artifact_id":"model_cassette.route.single_ir.test_source.m1_guideline_a.seed-42","artifact_kind":"model_cassette","canonicalization_policy_hash":"sha256:423e189facdecf68a7b2729e2d82e14e7b84f3cd699418a4f4dfe42124fe54c3","content_hash":"sha256:9003d14f8eec10fbababe89f3045e713902fdd8256fc5f7a8ea6d41f56f6c8d9","diagnostics":[],"evidence_status":"evidence_discovery_only","external_effects":["ai"],"input_hashes":[],"origin":"ai_generated","payload":{"constraint_hash":"sha256:0111668b2445286d22b069a8e51f6c517d4062b3b345f4d364f25dfb7970eaa0","model_identity":{"model_id":"qwen2.5-1.5b-instruct","quant":"int4","runtime_version":"openvino-genai-2026.2.1.0-3123-7dea0459b2a"},"output_hex":"","prompt":"Translate one Japanese clinical guideline document into a single ClinicalIR record.\u000a\u000aYou are given, for one source document, these input lines followed by the guideline text:\u000a- `document:` — the document id.\u000a- `segment:` — one line per upstream segment: its id, its kind, and the region ids it\u000a  covers.\u000a- `regions:` — every evidence region id of the document.\u000a- `system:` — the terminology system id.\u000a- `concept:` — one line per lexicon concept code; a `var=` mark names the context\u000a  variable that measures the concept, and `ge=`/`gt=`/`le=`/`lt=` marks give the\u000a  concept's canonical interval bounds over that variable.\u000a- `action:` — one line per action kind.\u000a\u000aProduce one JSON object that conforms to the supplied ClinicalIR schema. Follow these rules:\u000a\u000a- Draw every closed-vocabulary value from the lines above: binding `system` from the\u000a  `system:` line; binding `code`, each `alternatives` entry, statement concepts, and\u000a  action `target` values from the `concept:` lines; action `kind` values from the\u000a  `action:` lines; context `var` values from the `var=` marks. The remaining enumerated\u000a  fields — binding status, modality, strength, certainty — take their values from the\u000a  schema's own enumerations.\u000a- Record each terminology binding, clinical statement, action, context atom, quantity\u000a  interval, and exception clause the guideline expresses.\u000a- Cite evidence only by the supplied ids: place segment ids in `source_segment_ids` and\u000a  region ids in `region_ids`, using only ids that appear in the `segment:` and\u000a  `regions:` lines.\u000a- Give each generated id (`binding_id`, `statement_id`, `exception_id`) a fresh,\u000a  grammar-valid identifier.\u000a- Write every numeric interval bound as an integer inside the schema's range: copy a\u000a  concept's canonical bounds from its `ge=`/`gt=`/`le=`/`lt=` marks, and take the\u000a  numbers for an interval the text states directly from the text.\u000a\u000aOutput only the JSON object, with nothing before or after it.\u000a\u000adocument: test_source.m1_guideline_a\u000asegment: seg.0 kind=metadata regions=r.0\u000asegment: seg.1 kind=cq regions=r.1\u000asegment: seg.2 kind=recommendation regions=r.2\u000asegment: seg.3 kind=exception regions=r.3\u000asegment: seg.4 kind=metadata regions=r.4\u000asegment: seg.5 kind=table_row regions=r.5,r.6\u000asegment: seg.6 kind=definition regions=r.7,r.8\u000asegment: seg.7 kind=definition regions=r.10,r.9\u000asegment: seg.8 kind=definition regions=r.11,r.12\u000asegment: seg.9 kind=metadata regions=r.13\u000asegment: seg.10 kind=evidence regions=r.14\u000asegment: seg.11 kind=evidence regions=r.15\u000aregions: r.0,r.8,r.9,r.10,r.11,r.12,r.13,r.14,r.15,r.1,r.2,r.3,r.4,r.5,r.6,r.7\u000asystem: ckc.lex\u000aconcept: cond.sepsis\u000aconcept: cond.renal_severe\u000aconcept: cond.pregnancy\u000aconcept: drug.abx_a\u000aconcept: pop.adult var=q.age_years ge=18\u000aconcept: pop.child var=q.age_years lt=18\u000aaction: act.administer\u000a敗血症診療ガイドライン(合成)\u000aCQ1:成人の敗血症患者に対して抗菌薬Aを投与すべきか\u000a成人(18歳以上)の敗血症患者には抗菌薬Aを投与することを推奨する(強い推奨)。\u000aただし、重度腎機能障害のある患者を除く。\u000a用語の定義\u000a用語\u000a定義\u000a成人\u000a18歳以上の患者\u000a小児\u000a18歳未満の患者\u000a重度腎機能障害\u000a高度の腎機能低下を認める状態(合成定義)\u000aエビデンス\u000aランダム化比較試験2件(エビデンスの確実性:中)\u000a観察研究1件(エビデンスの確実性:低)","prompt_template_hash":"sha256:0439371e50d13d7dc1687b3cc5b64e1061dd602f541dc908a6a466385db8ea3a","route":"route.single_ir","seed":"42","source":"test_source.m1_guideline_a"},"producer":{"pipeline_id":"pipe.m2_single_ir","pipeline_step_id":"processing_stage.m2.model_fill","toolchain_manifest_hash":"sha256:66894b16254576f70fc56e3e3abf4d489c678e08feaec17e101ec405207b9d84"},"runtime_metadata":{},"schema_id":"schema.model_cassette","schema_version":"ckc.1","trace_refs":[]}